message.body: Ric! Hey, it's Kennedy from puppetyranny! Xander said you have a show tonight at 8. Headin back from Maine right now, we might just make it on time, if it's ok that we stay with y'all tonight. We can help you paint tha floor!
Absolutely, give me a ring when you're close. R!
So doesn't look like we'll get there in time for the show, but we'll come by the theatre after! Round 9:30/10?
